    "We also specifically selected notes from patients with at least one social work note.",
    "To further refine the selection, we considered notes with a note date one month before or after the patient's first social work note after it.",
    "For the MIMIC-III dataset, only notes written by physicians, social workers, and nurses were included for analysis.",
    "We focused on patients who had at least one social work note, without any specific date range criteria.",
    "Prior to annotation, all notes were segmented into sentences using the syntok 58 sentence segmenter as well as split into bullet points \"•\"."
